:"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32979,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/30\/ask-me-why-i-laughed\/","url_meta":{"origin":15706,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Will you ask me why I laughed?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 30, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman ibn Affan reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, call for water and perform ablution, then he laughed. The Prophet said, \u201cWill you not ask me what made me laugh?\u201d They said, \u201cWhat made you laugh, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17656,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/20\/beware-luxury\/","url_meta":{"origin":15706,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Extravagance: Believers do not live a life of luxury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, sent him to Yemen and he said, \u201cBeware of luxury, for the servants of Allah do not live luxuriously.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 22105 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0630\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","con